<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MTCNA Exam Simulator</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;600&display=swap');

  :root {
    --bg: #0d1117;
    --card: #161b22;
    --card2: #1c2128;
    --border: #30363d;
    --accent: #2f81f7;
    --accent2: #58a6ff;
    --text: #e6edf3;
    --muted: #8b949e;
    --correct: #238636;
    --correct-bg: #0d2819;
    --correct-text: #7ee787;
    --wrong: #da3633;
    --wrong-bg: #2d0f0f;
    --wrong-text: #ff7b72;
    --warn: #e85d26;
    --multi: #8b5cf6;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    background: var(--card);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0 24px;
    height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 20;
  }

  .logo {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--accent2);
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .logo span { color: var(--muted); }

  .h-sep { flex: 1; }

  .h-pill {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .pill-blue { background: rgba(47,129,247,.15); border-color: rgba(47,129,247,.3); color: var(--accent2); }
  .pill-purple { background: rgba(139,92,246,.15); border-color: rgba(139,92,246,.3); color: #c4b5fd; }

  #hTimer {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    min-width: 72px;
    text-align: center;
    display: none;
  }
  #hTimer.warn { color: var(--warn); border-color: var(--warn); }

  #hScore { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); display: none; }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  main { max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 20px 80px; }

  .screen { display: none; }
  .screen.active { display: block; }

  /* ── START SCREEN ── */
  .start-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 0 32px;
  }

  .start-hero h1 {
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .start-hero h1 em { color: var(--accent2); font-style: normal; }

  .start-hero p {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 28px;
  }

  .notice {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(139,92,246,.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,.25);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #c4b5fd;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .mod-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(160px, 1fr));
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .mod-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .15s;
    position: relative;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .mod-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .mod-card.sel { border-color: var(--accent2); background: rgba(88,166,255,.06); }

  .mod-card.sel::after {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    top: 9px; right: 11px;
    color: var(--accent2);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .mod-n { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--accent2); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .mod-t { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .mod-c { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); }

  .options-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .opt-btn {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-family: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .15s;
  }

  .opt-btn:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .opt-btn.active { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: #fff; }

  .start-note { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 24px; }

  .btn-start {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 13px 36px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .15s;
    letter-spacing: .3px;
  }
  .btn-start:hover { background: var(--accent2); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-start:disabled { opacity: .4; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }

  /* ── PROGRESS / QUIZ ── */
  .prog-wrap {
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--card2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .prog-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent2));
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: width .4s ease;
  }

  .q-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .q-num { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }

  .tag-row { display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .4px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }

  .tag-mod { background: rgba(47,129,247,.12); border-color: rgba(47,129,247,.25); color: var(--accent2); }
  .tag-multi { background: rgba(139,92,246,.12); border-color: rgba(139,92,246,.25); color: #c4b5fd; }
  .tag-tf { background: rgba(16,185,129,.12); border-color: rgba(16,185,129,.25); color: #6ee7b7; }

  .q-card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 24px 24px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .q-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .multi-hint {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #c4b5fd;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .multi-hint::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #8b5cf6;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .opts { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 9px; }

  .opt {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 13px 16px;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: inherit;
    color: var(--text);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .15s;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .opt:hover:not(:disabled):not(.checked) { background: var(--card2); border-color: var(--muted); }
  .opt:disabled { cursor: default; }

  .opt-lbl {
    min-width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    background: var(--card2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: all .15s;
  }

  /* checkbox style for multi */
  .opt-cb {
    min-width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 3px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all .15s;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .opt.checked .opt-cb { background: var(--multi); border-color: var(--multi); color: #fff; }
  .opt.checked { border-color: var(--multi); background: rgba(139,92,246,.06); }

  .opt.correct { background: var(--correct-bg); border-color: var(--correct); color: var(--correct-text); }
  .opt.correct .opt-lbl, .opt.correct .opt-cb { background: var(--correct); border-color: var(--correct); color: #fff; }

  .opt.wrong { background: var(--wrong-bg); border-color: var(--wrong); color: var(--wrong-text); }
  .opt.wrong .opt-lbl, .opt.wrong .opt-cb { background: var(--wrong); border-color: var(--wrong); color: #fff; }

  .opt.partial { background: rgba(232,93,38,.08); border-color: var(--warn); color: #fdba74; }
  .opt.partial .opt-lbl, .opt.partial .opt-cb { background: var(--warn); border-color: var(--warn); color: #fff; }

  .exp-box {
    margin-top: 14px;
    padding: 12px 15px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.03);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--muted);
    display: none;
  }
  .exp-box.show { display: block; }
  .exp-box strong { color: var(--text); }

  .multi-submit {
    margin-top: 12px;
    background: var(--multi);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 22px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .15s;
    display: none;
  }
  .multi-submit.show { display: inline-block; }
  .multi-submit:hover { background: #7c3aed; }

  .action-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-skip {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-family: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .15s;
  }
  .btn-skip:hover { color: var(--text); border-color: var(--muted); }

  .btn-next {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .15s;
    display: none;
  }
  .btn-next.show { display: inline-block; }
  .btn-next:hover { background: var(--accent2); }

  /* ── RESULT ── */
  .res-hero { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0 28px; }

  .res-ring {
    width: 130px;
    height: 130px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .res-ring svg { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; transform: rotate(-90deg); }

  .res-pct {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .res-lbl {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .5px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .res-verdict {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .res-verdict.pass { color: var(--correct-text); }
  .res-verdict.fail { color: var(--wrong-text); }

  .res-sub { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 24px; }

  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .stat {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 14px 10px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat .v {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }
  .stat .v.g { color: var(--correct-text); }
  .stat .v.r { color: var(--wrong-text); }
  .stat .v.b { color: var(--accent2); }
  .stat .l { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .5px; color: var(--muted); }

  .review { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 28px; }

  .review h3 {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .ri {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 13px 15px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .ri.ri-ok { border-left: 3px solid var(--correct); }
  .ri.ri-no { border-left: 3px solid var(--wrong); }
  .ri.ri-skip { border-left: 3px solid var(--border); }

  .ri .rq { font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 4px; color: var(--text); }
  .ri .ra { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }
  .ri .ra .ok { color: var(--correct-text); }
  .ri .ra .no { color: var(--wrong-text); }

  .res-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .res-actions button {
    padding: 12px 22px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: inherit;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all .15s;
  }

  .btn-again { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border: none; }
  .btn-again:hover { background: var(--accent2); }
  .btn-home2 { background: transparent; color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .btn-home2:hover { border-color: var(--muted); }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .q-text { font-size: 14px; }
    .mod-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo">MTCNA<span> Exam Simulator</span></div>
  <div class="h-sep"></div>
  <div class="h-pill pill-blue">RouterOS</div>
  <div class="h-pill pill-purple">Multi-Answer</div>
  <div id="hTimer">60:00</div>
</header>

<main>
  <!-- START -->
  <div class="screen active" id="sStart">
    <div class="start-hero">
      <h1>MTCNA <em>Exam Simulator</em></h1>
      <p>Questions styled after the real MikroTik MTCNA exam — English language, single & multiple-choice, scenario-based. Passing score: 60%.</p>
      <div class="notice">⚠️ Includes multiple-answer questions — select ALL correct options before submitting.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-label">Select Modules</div>
    <div class="mod-grid" id="modGrid"></div>

    <div class="section-label">Number of Questions</div>
    <div class="options-row" id="nRow">
      <button class="opt-btn active" data-n="10">10</button>
      <button class="opt-btn" data-n="20">20</button>
      <button class="opt-btn" data-n="25">25 (Exam)</button>
      <button class="opt-btn" data-n="all">All</button>
    </div>
    <div class="start-note" id="timerNote">Timer (60 min) activates in 25-question exam mode.</div>

    <br>
    <button class="btn-start" id="btnStart" onclick="startQuiz()">Start Exam →</button>
  </div>

  <!-- QUIZ -->
  <div class="screen" id="sQuiz">
    <div class="prog-wrap"><div class="prog-fill" id="progFill" style="width:0"></div></div>
    <div class="q-meta">
      <div class="q-num" id="qNum">1 / 25</div>
      <div class="tag-row" id="tagRow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="q-card">
      <div class="q-text" id="qText"></div>
      <div class="multi-hint" id="multiHint" style="display:none">Select all correct answers, then click Submit.</div>
      <div class="opts" id="opts"></div>
      <button class="multi-submit" id="multiSubmit" onclick="submitMulti()">Submit Answer</button>
      <div class="exp-box" id="expBox"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="action-row">
      <button class="btn-skip" onclick="skipQ()">Skip</button>
      <button class="btn-next show" id="btnNext" onclick="nextQ()" style="display:none">Next →</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- RESULT -->
  <div class="screen" id="sResult">
    <div class="res-hero">
      <div class="res-ring">
        <svg width="130" height="130" viewBox="0 0 130 130">
          <circle cx="65" cy="65" r="54" fill="none" stroke="#21262d" stroke-width="9"/>
          <circle id="ringArc" cx="65" cy="65" r="54" fill="none" stroke="#2f81f7" stroke-width="9"
            stroke-dasharray="339.3" stroke-dashoffset="339.3" stroke-linecap="round"
            style="transition:stroke-dashoffset 1s ease"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="res-pct" id="resPct">0%</div>
        <div class="res-lbl">Score</div>
      </div>
      <div class="res-verdict" id="resVerdict"></div>
      <div class="res-sub" id="resSub"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat"><div class="v g" id="stOk">0</div><div class="l">Correct</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="v r" id="stNo">0</div><div class="l">Wrong</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="v b" id="stSk">0</div><div class="l">Skipped</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="review">
      <h3>Answer Review</h3>
      <div id="reviewBox"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="res-actions">
      <button class="btn-again" onclick="retryQuiz()">Retry</button>
      <button class="btn-home2" onclick="goHome()">← Home</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<script>
// Q types: 'single' | 'multi' | 'tf'
// correct: index (single/tf) | array of indices (multi)
const BANK = [

  /* ══════════════ MODULE 1: INTRODUCTION ══════════════ */
  {mod:"M1 – Introduction", type:"single",
   q:"Which of the following best describes MikroTik RouterOS?",
   opts:["A proprietary RTOS developed by Cisco","A stand-alone Linux-based operating system for routing","A firmware only compatible with x86 hardware","A cloud-only network management platform"],
   correct:1, exp:"RouterOS is a stand-alone OS based on Linux kernel v3.3.5. It can run on RouterBOARD hardware, x86 PCs, or as a Virtual Machine."},

  {mod:"M1 – Introduction", type:"single",
   q:"A network technician needs to access a MikroTik router using a graphical interface from a Windows PC without knowing the router's IP address. Which tool should be used?",
   opts:["SSH client","Web browser (WebFig)","Winbox via MAC address","Serial console"],
   correct:2, exp:"Winbox can discover and connect to MikroTik routers via MAC address, which is useful when the IP address is unknown or unconfigured."},

  {mod:"M1 – Introduction", type:"multi",
   q:"Which of the following are valid methods to access and configure MikroTik RouterOS? (Select all that apply)",
   opts:["Winbox","Telnet","WebFig","Serial Console","RDP"],
   correct:[0,1,2,3], exp:"RouterOS can be accessed via Winbox, Telnet, SSH, WebFig (browser), and Serial Console. RDP is a Windows remote desktop protocol not supported by RouterOS."},

  {mod:"M1 – Introduction", type:"single",
   q:"What is the default RouterOS release channel recommended for production environments?",
   opts:["Beta (Release Candidate)","Long-term (Bugfix only)","Stable (Current)","Nightly build"],
   correct:1, exp:"Long-term is the most stable channel — it only receives bug fixes without new features, making it safest for production."},

  {mod:"M1 – Introduction", type:"tf",
   q:"True or False: A MikroTik RouterOS license is tied to the storage media (NAND) of the RouterBOARD device.",
   opts:["True","False"],
   correct:0, exp:"The license is stored on and tied to the NAND storage of the RouterBOARD. If you reinstall using a non-MikroTik tool, the license may be lost."},

  {mod:"M1 – Introduction", type:"single",
   q:"Which license level allows unlimited RouterOS features?",
   opts:["Level 3","Level 4","Level 5","Level 6"],
   correct:3, exp:"License Level 6 (Controller) provides unlimited RouterOS features. Level 3 is for CPE/station mode, Level 4 for AP use, Level 5 for ISP."},

  {mod:"M1 – Introduction", type:"single",
   q:"An administrator needs to completely reinstall RouterOS on a router that no longer boots. Which method should be used?",
   opts:["Soft reset via Winbox","Backup restore","Netinstall via network boot","CHR deployment"],
   correct:2, exp:"Netinstall boots the device via network (PXE-like) and allows full reinstallation of RouterOS even when the device cannot boot normally."},

  {mod:"M1 – Introduction", type:"multi",
   q:"Which of the following information is automatically obtained by a DHCP Client when it receives an IP lease? (Select all that apply)",
   opts:["IP Address","Subnet Mask","Default Gateway","DNS Server","MAC Address of the server"],
   correct:[0,1,2,3], exp:"DHCP provides IP address, subnet mask, default gateway, and DNS server. The server's MAC address is not delivered as part of the lease information."},

  {mod:"M1 – Introduction", type:"single",
   q:"A router's configuration is complex and the admin wants to restore it on a different RouterOS version. Which backup format should be used?",
   opts:["Binary backup file (.backup)","Script export file (.rsc)","ZIP archive","Plain text log file"],
   correct:1, exp:"Script files (.rsc) contain RouterOS CLI commands in plain text and can be used across different RouterOS versions. Binary backups are version-specific."},

  {mod:"M1 – Introduction", type:"single",
   q:"Which IP address range is NOT considered a private (RFC 1918) address space?",
